{"tid":684054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世界盃最受歡迎波衫排行：尼日利亞球衣最受歡迎","createTime":"2018-05-30T08:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T09:23:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"23b3c1c3ebbd01c6ed12935a71fc68fe7b295d0a","tid":684054,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"2018年05月30日13:47<br />\n<br />\n　　世界盃臨近天空體育發起了一項投票活動，選出你最喜愛的國家隊波衫，目前尼日利亞隊的綠色球衣暫居榜首。<br />\n<br />\n　　前十名：<br />\n1、尼日利亞（38.8k）<br />\n2、德國（20.8k）<br />\n3、澳州（16.8k）<br />\n4、英格蘭（15.8k）<br />\n5、瑞士（14k）<br />\n6、比利時（14k）<br />\n7、法國（14k）<br />\n8、巴西（13.8k）<br />\n9、哥倫比亞（13.4k）<br />\n10、克羅地亞（13k）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　目前，投票仍在進行，球迷們可以在天空體育官網上進行投票，不同於其他投票，球迷可以pick多支球隊並且無需註冊。"},{"pid":"e0dcdbe2c3a339042f6301e8698dca9710bc22f5","tid":684054,"uid":111751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"36ebf2cef376d72a193ff3ae9c83cc2e6855d744","tid":684054,"uid":53672,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"二和b仲吸引過果d乜鬼美斯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc013c1b1c016d324af41ad1a6c577d1151e96b","tid":684054,"uid":137361,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bea3e84b320405e5b772c002825feff6e4bb7065","tid":684054,"uid":35637,"like":155,"dislike":5,"score":150,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c1.hoopchina.com.cn/uploads/images/20180208/13/61cf459c52e09e0cdf825645e07d9543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F20180208%2F13%2F61cf459c52e09e0cdf825645e07d9543.jpg&h=1b155695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d386353e38a1e542bbb4c7b5bcd99c8d453f143d","tid":684054,"uid":58552,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"quote":{"pid":"be